messages.text: Hey babe, almost ready for dinner?
Good things come to those who are patient ;)
Waiting has never been my fortè. I’m a visceral creature...
What say you we skip dinner?
Haha no way, we have to go, Chey and Asad hooked us up with these reservations.
Fuck them, and fuck you too ;)
Okay, keep it in your pants buddy haha
Be a little civil at dinner, okay?
Jake, this isn’t funny, we’re gonna be late.
Where? I’m on my driveway and it’s pitch black outside. No car.
I’m going inside. Text me when you’re actually outside.
I swear to God, Jake, where are you?!
I was outside. You wasted your opportunity.
I’m calling Chey and Asad and saying I’m sick.
Better than explaining that my boyfriend’s a dick.
That’s the way I like it.
What the hell is wrong with you today…
Baby, I’m sorry, it was a bad joke.
Baby, don’t be like this. I love you.
I love you too. And yeah, it was a really shitty joke.
I’ll make it up to you.
Who cares about Chey and Asad?
Chey and Asad don’t seem too mad.
They probably want each other for themselves.
Like I want you for myself.
After being an asshole, you sure do like to keep fooling around.
Where the hell are you, anyway?
Um, I don’t like this game.
ha ha ha hahaha haha ha haaa
I can fucking hear you. You’re freaking me out.
Jack - you’re scaring me. Get out.
I don’t know if you’re high or what, but…
You need to stop talking like this, okay Jake?
I don’t want to play anymore.
I THOUGHT YOU WANTED TO PLAY HAHHAHA
Don’t worry baby, I’ll make him smile.
Look, I’ll give you money, whatever. Just don’t hurt him.
It’s just a little poetry to heat up our evening.
I told you I would heat up our evening.
I told you I would make him smile.
Then let my boyfriend go. I’m calling the police.
I DONT LIKE TO FROWN ALEXA
They’re coming for you, dumbass. Tracked GPS from Jake's phone.
And I hope you burn in hell.
